      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. Be a permanent **resident of Gujarat**1. Be a **woman**1. Belong to the **Rabari or Bharwad caste**1. Belong to a **socially and educationally backward class** as recognized by the Government of Gujarat1. Be between **21 to 45 years** of age1. Have a **total annual family** income not exceeding **₹3.00 lakh**1. Intend to start your **own business or self-employment** venture using the loan\n",
